text: Franco Bonato (born 2 October 1925) is a Venezuelan former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Venezuelan male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Venezuela Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bassano del Grappa Category:Italian emigrants to Venezuela
